osyfe.tool

Class Remotery

  • java.lang.Object
    • osyfe.tool.Remotery

  • public class Remotery
extends java.lang.Object
    A profiling tool. The Screen class defines some basic frames if enabled.
    The corresponding viewer can be found in the utilities.
